ZH: 我决定捐献一部分工资给慈善机构。
EN: I have decided to donate a portion of my salary to a charity organization.

ZH: 在这个困难的时期，捐献血液是非常重要的。
EN: Donating blood is very important during this difficult time.

ZH: 我们应该鼓励更多人参与器官捐献。
EN: We should encourage more people to participate in organ donation.

ZH: 捐献食物给贫困家庭是一种善举。
EN: Donating food to needy families is a kind deed.

ZH: 他每年都会捐献一部分收入给慈善机构。
EN: He donates a portion of his income to charity organizations every year.

ZH: 志愿者们积极捐献时间和精力来帮助需要帮助的人。
EN: Volunteers actively donate their time and energy to help those in need.

ZH: 我很感激那些自愿捐献眼角膜的人。
EN: I am grateful to those who voluntarily donate their corneas.

ZH: 捐献器官可以拯救许多生命。
EN: Donating organs can save many lives.

ZH: 我们应该鼓励更多人参与献血行动。
EN: We should encourage more people to participate in blood donation drives.

ZH: 她经常捐献不要的衣物给慈善组织。
EN: She often donates unwanted clothes to charitable organizations.

